definitions.definition: A suburban village in Nursling and Rownhams parish, Test Valley district, Hampshire , England , just outside the City of Southampton ( OS grid ref SU3817 ) .
A service area on the M27 motorway to the east of the village ( OS grid ref SU3917 ) .
